---
title: Bacon and Caramelised Onion Cheeseburger with truffled wedges and baby gem salad
description: This bacon cheeseburger is a decadent dinner option piled high with premium ingredients. Truffled wedges, caramelised onions and a tart yet fresh salad make for an abundant and inviting meal.
